{"tid":2148152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Biden 幕僚 ‘澄清’: 「對中國的關稅，未有定論。」","createTime":"2020-08-09T17:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T05:31:02.000Z","uid":226548,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64fc7228e1f4c7a9fcba84c0122c8ff3f8b605db","tid":2148152,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PVXWB_8O9MSSYIHm1e8pS0CgZeM=/640x411/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IVZA4T67C4LOQMT6N6QRT37LHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPVXWB_8O9MSSYIHm1e8pS0CgZeM%3D%2F640x411%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIVZA4T67C4LOQMT6N6QRT37LHY.jpg&h=dc769bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，特朗普選情回穩，和打「中國牌」有關。不少美國人認同他的對華立場，認為可以反制中國影響力。不過，拜登在接受美國《全國公共電台》（NPR）專訪，<strong><span class=\"red\">被主持人問到會否延續對華關稅措施時，他表示不會</span></strong>，更反問：「誰說特朗普的立場是好的？」<br />\n<br />\n拜登指出，特朗普的關稅措施，令美國的製造業陷入衰退，對農業造成數以十億美元計的損失，而最後都是由納稅人去埋單。他又補充表示，美國正以錯誤的方法去追擊中國。不過，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">拜登的幕僚事後澄清，對於拜登當選後會否取消對華關稅尚未有定論</span></span></strong>，但拜登立場不變，一上任就會重新評估關稅。<br />\n<br />\n拜登去年5月批評特朗普對華掀起貿易戰時，亦曾質疑中國是否「吃美國免費午餐」，又斷言中國不是美國的競爭對象。他在NPR的訪問中，也強調自己比特朗普更認識中國，曾花了許多時間和中國國家主席習近平打交道。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">拜登的確是第一位與習近平深入交流的美國政治領袖</span></strong>，兩人曾分別擔任美中兩國的副總統和副主席，在多次互訪中深入接觸。據記錄，自2011年年初開始，在之後的年半時間內，兩人在美中兩地至少見了8次面。除了正式會晤，還一起散步、在農村學校打籃球，在僅有翻譯陪同下，<strong><span class=\"red\">私下共同進餐合計超過25小時</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"71f0e68a22f1c1a7ccc0598467305b2d6c04fa35","tid":2148152,"uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200808/BHGHBE6UIVXNTB6WAVTSY6M4TI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200808%2FBHGHBE6UIVXNTB6WAVTSY6M4TI%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=683fcfee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200808%2FBHGHBE6UIVXNTB6WAVTSY6M4TI%2F&h=36372ac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200808/BHGHBE6UIVXNTB6WAVTSY6M4TI/</a>"},{"pid":"c85c404ab7b21bac7c5a552d9642de08e2c9a81c","tid":2148152,"uid":152559,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣老人痴呆奶硬共, 唔可以比佢當選"},{"pid":"1febc8c089c30022ee41129cd83182165b75fc1d","tid":2148152,"uid":206522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"64fc7228e1f4c7a9fcba84c0122c8ff3f8b605db","tid":2148152,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PVXWB_8O9MSSYIHm1e8pS0CgZeM=/640x411/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IVZA4T67C4LOQMT6N6QRT37LHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPVXWB_8O9MSSYIHm1e8pS0CgZeM%3D%2F640x411%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIVZA4T67C4LOQMT6N6QRT37LHY.jpg&h=dc769bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，特朗普選情回穩，和打「中國牌」有關。不少美國人認同他的對華立場，認為可以反制中國影響力。不過，拜登在接受美國《全國公共電台》（NPR）專訪，<strong><span class=\"red\">被主持人問到會否延續對華關稅措施時，他表示不會</span></strong>，更反問：「誰說特朗普的立場是好的？」<br />\n<br />\n拜登指出，特朗普的關稅措施，令美國的製造業陷入衰退，對農業造成數以十億美元計的損失，而最後都是由納稅人去埋單。他又補充表示，美國正以錯誤的方法去追擊中國。不過，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">拜登的幕僚事後澄清，對於拜登當選後會否取消對華關稅尚未有定論</span></span></strong>，但拜登立場不變，一上任就會重新評估關稅。<br />\n<br />\n拜登去年5月批評特朗普對華掀起貿易戰時，亦曾質疑中國是否「吃美國免費午餐」，又斷言中國不是美國的競爭對象。他在NPR的訪問中，也強調自己比特朗普更認識中國，曾花了許多時間和中國國家主席習近平打交道。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">拜登的確是第一位與習近平深入交流的美國政治領袖</span></strong>，兩人曾分別擔任美中兩國的副總統和副主席，在多次互訪中深入接觸。據記錄，自2011年年初開始，在之後的年半時間內，兩人在美中兩地至少見了8次面。除了正式會晤，還一起散步、在農村學校打籃球，在僅有翻譯陪同下，<strong><span class=\"red\">私下共同進餐合計超過25小時</span></strong>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"25小時 乜幼幼都玩哂啦"},{"pid":"f4014951310bf07d1f2379c4ea3ade39eb094581","tid":2148152,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"佢自己親口講奶共喎，點信你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0e6d3387cfca4dd55dfe09a7fa8b39ba239b58","tid":2148152,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9TKT1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9TKT1O.jpg&h=bf782356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師傅一年前已經同我講過， 佢話「<span class=\"green\">侵會贏</span>，但唔可以太劇烈運動，加上餵人奶要食番多啲嘢，如果唔係唔夠奶。」"},{"pid":"8255aac97d875b46cf738f2c84dd719a6bdadcc9","tid":2148152,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa3073eb53da79f4cad1249bb07b2a621dac427","tid":2148152,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:19:35.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9cabcb90abff9e4ea7acfd77605ce063ddf56d","tid":2148152,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:22:16.000Z","msg":"一痴中共, 真係會自動變弱智, 民主黨就係好例子"},{"pid":"09b434183a4e76f3b8012b5ddd5e7af03044fbeb","tid":2148152,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}